00:28:32,759 --> 00:28:38,859
And it's just so brilliant because the whole community comes to watch

526
00:28:38,859 --> 00:28:43,099
the Abalones play local teams in footy.

527
00:28:43,099 --> 00:28:49,000
So I just think we do great stuff in the AFL.

528
00:28:49,799 --> 00:28:54,619
And if you can be part of that as an organisation, that's quite fulfilling.

529
00:28:55,039 --> 00:28:56,019
What a brilliant name for a team.

530
00:28:56,119 --> 00:28:56,599
The Abalones.

531
00:28:57,460 --> 00:28:58,579
I'd like to see them play one day.

