00:29:30,359 --> 00:29:32,099
Breath test people on the way in.

546
00:29:33,160 --> 00:29:34,059
And then go.

547
00:29:34,480 --> 00:29:37,839
You know, because it's just, it's one of those, it's, you know,

548
00:29:37,900 --> 00:29:41,480
it's what footy does, which I think is bring communities together.

549
00:29:41,660 --> 00:29:43,819
And that's why I love the involvement of the AFL.

550
00:29:44,140 --> 00:29:46,079
We love going and seeing the elite men and women.

551
00:29:47,220 --> 00:29:50,039
And, you know, you're lucky enough to have played

552
00:29:50,039 --> 00:29:53,880
and been a very good player at that level and would have met amazing people.

553
00:29:54,519 --> 00:29:57,380
But footy's big in the community.

554
00:29:57,380 --> 00:30:00,339
And if you haven't been to a country footy game and, you know,

