00:30:30,359 --> 00:30:33,559
And Colin Carter, and you know Colin,

566
00:30:33,680 --> 00:30:37,680
an AFL commissioner, chairman of Geelong, was on the trip.

567
00:30:38,099 --> 00:30:40,059
And he was a director of West Farmers at the time.

568
00:30:40,660 --> 00:30:43,720
And this local community that we flew into had heard

569
00:30:43,720 --> 00:30:45,759
that this Geelong person was coming.

570
00:30:45,819 --> 00:30:48,640
So they all expected a Geelong AFL player.

