and take us as players out to remote communities and you'd stay out for a week.

582
00:31:23,160 --> 00:31:25,779
Literally forged these relationships where you could come back

583
00:31:25,779 --> 00:31:28,380
and someone would take your name, you know, and you'd come back

584
00:31:28,380 --> 00:31:30,339
and you'd meet Luke Darcy.

