00:36:30,199 --> 00:36:30,900
It can fill the role.

691
00:36:30,980 --> 00:36:31,619
Has that become challenging?

692
00:36:32,000 --> 00:36:36,219
Well, hopefully the candidates have all had enough feedback from me

693
00:36:36,219 --> 00:36:38,480
and others on where the process is at.

694
00:36:40,039 --> 00:36:43,679
Yeah, there's, as you know, last year we did media rights.

695
00:36:44,079 --> 00:36:45,119
As I said, the Hawthorne thing,

