00:37:35,920 --> 00:37:39,519
The record of Gil and the rights and the AFL's health

711
00:37:39,519 --> 00:37:40,980
and coming through that speaks for itself.

712
00:37:41,159 --> 00:37:45,000
And I think everyone in our industry can't be anything apart from universally

713
00:37:45,000 --> 00:37:48,139
admiring the role that Gil's played.

714
00:37:48,340 --> 00:37:51,800
And, you know, I love that you're enjoying the time.

715
00:37:51,920 --> 00:37:53,019
I find that interesting.

716
00:37:53,139 --> 00:37:55,159
We see, you know, in a lot of the roles you're in,

717
00:37:55,500 --> 00:37:57,800
leaders are really conscious of how they share the vision

718
00:37:57,800 --> 00:37:59,579
for what they want to do.

